410
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,479
In my eyes,

411
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,520
you are Lu Jiu.

412
00:18:42,599 --> 00:18:43,560
Not Fei Ying.

413
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,880
You really don't mind?

414
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,239
