415
00:18:47,439 --> 00:18:48,959
where we are born.

416
00:18:49,199 --> 00:18:50,439
Now that you have a chance

417
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:51,839
to choose again,

418
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:54,280
you must live the life you truly want.

419
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,760
Lin Lang.

420
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:06,760
