421
00:19:07,479 --> 00:19:08,479
Nothing.

422
00:19:09,079 --> 00:19:09,959
Really.

423
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:11,079
Really.

424
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:12,560
Lu Jiu.

425
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,199
