448
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,680
Engaged? What are you talking about?

449
00:19:55,719 --> 00:19:56,959
There's nothing like that at all.

450
00:19:57,839 --> 00:20:00,239
You're just one step away from admitting it.

451
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:01,560
Here I have

452
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,359
