454
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,439
your whole room will be filled with fragrance.

455
00:20:06,599 --> 00:20:08,400
It'll make you feel like you're in a dream.

456
00:20:08,479 --> 00:20:09,680
Perfume?

457
00:20:15,239 --> 00:20:17,599
I like you even more.

458
00:20:23,239 --> 00:20:23,839
Miss

459
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,680
Linlang, do you want it or not?

460
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,000
Linlang

461
00:20:27,239 --> 00:20:28,280
