464
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:32,319
Actually, I...

465
00:20:33,719 --> 00:20:34,479
Linlang

466
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:35,640
Are you okay?

467
00:20:36,479 --> 00:20:37,680
