489
00:21:23,199 --> 00:21:24,839
It's just a small matter, no need to worry.

490
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:27,199
My father taught me from a young age

491
00:21:27,239 --> 00:21:29,040
to take responsibility for my own actions.

492
00:21:29,479 --> 00:21:30,640
Please accept it.

493
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:31,719
Linlang.

494
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:33,839
Since Miss Xing'er won't accept it,

495
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,000
if you force it on her,

496
00:21:35,199 --> 00:21:36,400
it will seem like you're just seeking praise.

497
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:37,359
How about this instead?

498
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:38,920
Let's go inside and buy something.

499
00:21:39,119 --> 00:21:39,640
This way,

500
00:21:39,719 --> 00:21:41,800
Miss Xing'er can accept the money with peace of mind.

501
00:21:42,479 --> 00:21:43,280
Let's go.

502
00:21:53,439 --> 00:21:54,160
Go ahead.

503
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:55,760
