518
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,880
Alright, let's get serious.

519
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,640
I noticed on her

520
00:22:24,079 --> 00:22:25,959
the scent of Sima Kong's sachet.

521
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:28,319
You mean

522
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,680
