527
00:22:38,839 --> 00:22:40,520
That's not something a merchant would do.

528
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:48,359
The people from the temple just took some fabric from here.

529
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,000
So,

530
00:22:50,199 --> 00:22:52,280
this silk shop and the temple

531
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:54,479
are both places where they exchange information.

532
00:22:56,599 --> 00:22:57,880
Have you two made your choice?

533
00:22:58,560 --> 00:23:00,640
All the fabrics here are so beautiful.

534
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,719
Why don't you recommend one for me?

535
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:05,119
This young lady has a spirited look.

536
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:07,040
Complicated patterns don't suit you.

537
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:09,040
But this one

538
00:23:09,239 --> 00:23:11,160
is simple and neat, yet still charming.

539
00:23:11,239 --> 00:23:12,160
It really suits you.

540
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,599
You run such a large silk shop,

541
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:16,160
