545
00:23:23,839 --> 00:23:25,560
Of course, I save wherever I can.

546
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:27,079
Calluses from sewing

547
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,680
should be on the fingertips.

548
00:23:29,079 --> 00:23:30,280
But your calluses

549
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,560
