570
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:15,439
It's clear you're not a bad person.

571
00:24:16,319 --> 00:24:18,040
Do you think I'll let you go just because of that?

572
00:24:18,119 --> 00:24:20,520
A person's posture is shaped by their environment.

573
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:22,239
Even though you're dressed in fine clothes,

574
00:24:22,439 --> 00:24:23,800
your spine leans forward.

575
00:24:24,479 --> 00:24:27,040
It shows you often bow and bend over.

576
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:28,520
You are under someone's control.

577
00:24:28,839 --> 00:24:30,040
Who exactly are you people?

578
00:24:30,119 --> 00:24:31,439
Who we are doesn't matter.

579
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:33,239
What matters is letting those innocent people

580
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:34,040
regain their freedom

581
00:24:34,119 --> 00:24:35,160
and reunite with their families.

582
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:40,839
Oh no.

583
00:24:46,119 --> 00:24:47,280
I won't kill you this time.

584
00:24:47,359 --> 00:24:49,000
But don't let me see you again.

585
00:24:49,079 --> 00:24:49,959
Everyone has their own fate.

586
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:51,400
This is their destiny.

587
00:24:51,479 --> 00:24:52,760
Don't meddle in other people's business.

588
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:53,839
But...

589
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,079
They went out that way.

590
00:25:01,239 --> 00:25:02,000
Chase them.

591
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:06,880
Go after them.

592
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,040
She let us go just like that.

593
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:13,520
Could there be any danger?

594
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,640
Probably not.

595
00:25:14,719 --> 00:25:16,439
Judging by her demeanor, her status isn't low.

596
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:17,760
She'll naturally have a way to handle it.

597
00:25:18,079 --> 00:25:18,920
It's just that...

598
00:25:19,199 --> 00:25:20,880
Our intention to rescue someone is too obvious now.

599
00:25:21,119 --> 00:25:22,880
We need to find a way to act quickly.

600
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:25,599
I've got it.

601
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,400
This silk shop is just like the temple.

602
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,119
They're both places where information is exchanged.

603
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,920
As long as we find someone connected to both places,

604
00:25:30,959 --> 00:25:32,119
someone who has contact with both,

605
00:25:32,199 --> 00:25:33,520
we can find a breakthrough.

606
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:34,760
Let's go.

607
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,160
You're very lucky.

608
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:45,239
Someone can come to save you.

609
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,920
But who can come to save me?

610
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:16,400
Found her.

611
00:27:46,239 --> 00:27:47,000
Master.

612
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,839
Xing'er has been acting very strange lately.

613
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,479
You can't let your guard down.

614
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:55,359
Hmm.

615
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:58,079
Just keep a close eye on her.

616
00:27:58,760 --> 00:28:00,719
She doesn't have any household registration papers.

617
00:28:01,079 --> 00:28:02,439
She can't escape Mist Town.

618
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,119
Besides,

619
00:28:05,719 --> 00:28:07,920
she still thinks her younger brother

620
00:28:08,199 --> 00:28:10,000
is in my hands.

621
00:28:10,439 --> 00:28:13,079
She would never dare betray me.

622
00:28:13,199 --> 00:28:14,239
Master, you are wise.

623
00:28:14,520 --> 00:28:16,079
She would never even dream

624
00:28:16,119 --> 00:28:17,560
that brat

625
00:28:17,599 --> 00:28:18,640
actually, years ago

626
00:28:18,719 --> 00:28:19,680
fell ill

627
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:20,760
and died.

628
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:24,800
If she really notices anything unusual,

629
00:28:24,959 --> 00:28:27,199
you'll take her place.

630
00:28:27,239 --> 00:28:28,359
Thank you, Master.

631
00:28:28,560 --> 00:28:30,319
About Xing'er...

632
00:28:30,439 --> 00:28:32,040
That girl Xing'er,

633
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:34,239
she's still got some looks.

634
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,520
Sell her to the brothel.

635
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:39,199
Maybe we can get a good price.

636
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,680
Master, I've followed you for so many years,

637
00:28:41,719 --> 00:28:43,319
but I've never tasted a woman.

638
00:28:43,439 --> 00:28:45,359
Before selling Xing'er to the brothel,

639
00:28:45,439 --> 00:28:46,640
could I...

640
00:28:47,079 --> 00:28:47,839
How dare you!

641
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,079
Spare me, Master!

642
00:28:55,479 --> 00:28:56,359
Don't be afraid.

643
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,680
Giving her to you

644
00:28:59,079 --> 00:29:00,760
isn't out of the question.

645
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:02,880
Thank you, Master.

646
00:29:29,599 --> 00:29:31,520
Master, you've been hit by a dart!

647
00:29:34,599 --> 00:29:35,920
Master! Master, this...

648
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,439
What should we do?

649
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:44,719
You two

650
00:29:46,119 --> 00:29:47,000
Who are you?

651
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:50,680
You saved us.

652
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:51,800
Come with me.

653
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:09,640
Miss Xu has already made all the arrangements.

654
00:30:09,839 --> 00:30:10,839
Over at the temple

655
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,160
there's still no news.

656
00:30:13,439 --> 00:30:14,800
We made it through today safely.

657
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:15,839
Thanks to you.

658
00:30:15,959 --> 00:30:16,959
It's just my duty.

659
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,760
Young Master hates anything wrinkled the most.

660
00:30:29,479 --> 00:30:31,199
Sima Kong is such a clean person.

661
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,479
Now

662
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:34,199
he's locked up in that place.

663
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:35,800
It's really hard for him.

664
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:45,640
If only he had listened to me earlier,

665
00:30:45,839 --> 00:30:47,680
he wouldn't be in this situation now.

666
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:49,839
It's only been a few days since Sima Kong was captured.

667
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,040
Linlang and I

668
00:30:51,239 --> 00:30:52,719
haven't told anyone yet.

669
00:30:52,839 --> 00:30:54,359
But you were able to come and rescue him right away.

670
00:30:54,479 --> 00:30:55,640
Who exactly are you?

671
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:58,719
Does this have anything to do with you saving him?

672
00:31:03,079 --> 00:31:03,959
Indeed.

673
00:31:06,599 --> 00:31:08,000
I don't care what his status is.

674
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:08,800
Right now,

675
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,839
he is my friend.

676
00:31:09,959 --> 00:31:11,319
So I will risk my life to save him.

677
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:15,439
It seems my young master truly has good judgment.

678
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,880
I was the one who judged with a petty mind,

679
00:31:18,959 --> 00:31:20,479
doubting a gentleman's intentions.

680
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:22,239
I can tell

681
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,520
you treat him very well.

682
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,719
You two are friends as well, aren't you?

683
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,760
How could I dare call myself the young master's friend?

684
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:28,199
I'm just his servant.

685
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:31,280
Though the young master seems distant on the surface,

686
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,839
he is actually kind-hearted.

687
00:31:32,959 --> 00:31:34,000
All these years,

688
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,640
he has never treated me harshly.

689
00:31:35,959 --> 00:31:37,439
I'm simply repaying his kindness.

690
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:38,719
By the way,

691
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,479
about that plan—

692
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,959
is it actually feasible?

693
00:31:42,199 --> 00:31:43,800
According to the information I received,

694
00:31:44,119 --> 00:31:45,599
the one coming for the deal tomorrow

695
00:31:45,760 --> 00:31:47,280
is the wealthy Shanxi merchant

696
00:31:47,439 --> 00:31:49,079
Hua Jinshen's eldest daughter.

697
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:50,160
Miss Hua.

698
00:31:50,359 --> 00:31:51,839
No one has ever seen her true face.

699
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:53,719
I've had my people intercept them.

700
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:54,839
Those thieves

701
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,199
shouldn't notice.

702
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:57,920
That's true,

703
00:31:58,079 --> 00:31:59,079
but

704
00:31:59,599 --> 00:32:02,079
having Linlang pretend to be a noble lady

705
00:32:03,239 --> 00:32:04,920
is indeed a bit difficult for her.

706
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,520
Who says it's difficult for me?

707
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:12,839
Look.
